Mg_FiringRange_easy

minigame where you have to shoot targets before they reach shooting zone, players have unlimited ammo so you dont nee to worry about reloading :)... map has 4 different kind of targets
1. soldier (health 800 speed 20)
2. bomber (health 400 speed 30 + explodes (dont let too close))
3. tank (healt 2400 speed 10)
4. helicopter (health 10000 (final boss) speed 10)

hope you like it
